message.content: The likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper are "cs.AI", "cs.DB", "cs.CL", "cs.LG", and "cs.IR". This is because the paper discusses a method for question answering over knowledge bases, which is a topic that falls under the intersection of artificial intelligence (cs.AI), databases (cs.DB), natural language processing (cs.CL), machine learning (cs.LG), and information retrieval (cs.IR).
